Siemens Names Mark Albenze CEO of Wind Operations for Americas

-- B y   Z a c h a r y   T r a c e r
-- 
2011-09-27T15:37:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/siemens-names-mark-albenze-ceo-of-wind-operations-for-americas.html
Siemens AG (SIE) ,  Europe ’s largest
engineering company, has appointed Mark Albenze to run its wind-
power business in the Americas, the company said in an e-mailed
statement.   Albenze, who was previously a vice president at Siemens
Energy Inc., was named chief executive officer of Siemens’s wind
business unit for the Americas, based in  Orlando ,  Florida .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zachary Tracer in New York at 
 ztracer1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
